name: Smart Send Shipping for WooCommerce
author: SafeDigit

sections.description:
Seamlessly integrate shipping for your Australian business with WooCommerce and the Smart Send shipping plugin.

Awesome shipping rates thanks to Smart Send’s bulk discount through its carriers, plus Smart Send provides timely resolution of any shipping issues should they occur to save your business time and effort.

Allows customers to get an accurate quote for shipping before checking out, simply by entering some basic address info. You can offer cheapest shipping quote or multiple shipping price point options at checkout; with additional options like signature on delivery, transport assurance to cover goods against loss/damage in transit, tail-lift truck options for heavy/bulky items AND the ability to set handling fees via flat rate or percentage.

Merchants can fulfill shipping directly from within the WooCommerce ‘orders’ section of the dashboard, specifying pickup date and time which instantly notifies couriers when to arrive and collect your shipments.

This plugin requires the WooCommerce e-commerce plugin.

Fulfillment, Shipping Classes

You can instruct the plugin to request shipping quotes based on the packing the product comes in or on instructions you specify.

Support

Support is available via the Smart Send website;
sections.installation:
1. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
  2. Under Woocommerce -> Settings -> Shipping, find the Smart Send section and fill out the required fields. You will need a Smart Send VIP account.
sections.faq:
Do I need a Smart Send VIP account to use the plugin?

Yes, you need a Paid VIP plan with Smart Send. You can sign up here:
[https://www.smartsend.com.au/vip-plans.cfm]

sections.reviews:
Very good plugin for Australia Ecommerce website

By inspiretk on January 11, 2017

Very good plugin. Works good. Saved me a ton of time. Shipping prices is VERY competitive. Highly recommended! My products have weight and dimensions. The plugin auto detects it and calculates the shipping automatically. Has different rates for different shipping speed, depending on what the Customer wants. When you set up this plugin, you can request for a free testing account from Smartsend. They'll reply back to you within a day as in my situation with your testing account login. Once you've set it up, it will work. Once you're happy with the plugin, ask for a real live account. They set it up for you free. You just have to prepay your account. You do this when you've made a sale. In my case, I had to prepaid $100 as a minimum, which is fine with me. You just top up your account when you need to. If you need support from them, they answer very fast. Great service, great people. You'll need to ignore the plugin being updated long time ago. It's a working plugin, that's why it's not being updated, as it's already working. Good luck to you.
